Subject: [PATCH 1/2] B3 V2: Enhanced Backtester mit 9-Dim Risk-Scoring
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Neues Feature: run_backtest_v2() mit vollem 9-Dim-Scoring:
- 6 echte Dimensionen (technical_breakdown, volume_divergence,
  peer_weakness, valuation_percentile, macro_regime, options_skew-stub)
  + 3 Stubs mit reduziertem Gewicht (matching live risk_scorer)
- Vol-Targeting in Position-Sizing (TARGET_VOL=18%)
- Cash-Floor (20%) Enforcement
- Sector-Concentration-Cap (40%)
- Daily-Loss-Brake (-5%)
- Multi-Horizon Strategy Labels (long_term vs mid_term)
- Per-Trade-Tracking mit detaillierten Records
- Sortino, Calmar, Avg-Holding-Days in Result
- Regime-History-Tracking im adaptive-Mode

CLI: scripts/backtest.py --v2 --compare-strategies
V1 bleibt vollständig backward-compatible.

Tests: 16 neue Tests (test_backtest_v2.py), alle grün.
  - Unit-Tests für alle 9-Dim-Scoring-Funktionen
  - Integration-Tests für V2 engine (static + adaptive)
  - Cash-Floor + Vol-Targeting-Validierung
  - V1-Backward-Compatibility-Check
